trans-unit.source: Interacts with the parser to build a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell" /> control.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCellControlBuilder> class is used primarily by control developers.

trans-unit.source: To create a custom control builder for a control that is derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell> class, you must inherit from this class.
trans-unit.target: 若要创建派生自的控件的自定义控件生成器<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell>必须从此类继承的类。

trans-unit.source: Specifies whether white space literals are allowed.
trans-unit.target: 指定是否允许空白文本。
